agency_name: Department of Agriculture and Consumer Services
series_description: This series documents the disposition of unprocessed peanuts that are inspected at the buying point before being stored. This series may include, but is not limited to: completed farmer certificates, note sheets, and correspondence.
retention_statement: 3 Years after end of state fiscal year

agency_name: Department of Agriculture and Consumer Services
series_description: This series documents milled peanut inspections. This series may include, but is not limited to: requests for inspection/reinspection, note sheets, and correspondence
retention_statement: 3 Years after end of state fiscal year

agency_name: Department of Agriculture and Consumer Services
series_description: This series documents the grading of peanuts before arriving a mill for shelling and sizing. This series may include, but is limited to: regrade note sheets, reports, and correspondence.
retention_statement: 3 Years after end of state fiscal year
